name: Are We There Yet
description:
The “Are we there yet ? “project is a collaboration with writer Natalie Baker. 

It is a fiction about the journey of a community of which’s Island disappeared due to the sudden rise of the sea. They had to build their new home, which could walk through deserts, montains and oceans. As they are traveling, they collect memories and objects, and share their stories wherever they land. 

This design is a mixed of 3D modeling and scanned hand drawing.
